Remember the Giants? Big Blue is back in action following the bye week, taking
the field Sunday night to face the Packers in a rematch of last year's NFC
divisional round at MetLife Stadium. Kickoff is set for 8:20 p.m. but you can
join us here around 7 p.m. MOBILE USERS: FOLLOW ...
headline: LIVE: Giants vs. Packers, Sun. night, 8:20 p.m. (NY Daily News)
